            <abstract>
                <p>Protective prayer against the evil action described as 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʿayn</foreign> (‘evil eye’) of 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ṭǝlā</foreign>, which may be an abbreviated form of 
                    <foreign xml:lang="am">ṣǝlā wagi</foreign> (literally: ‘piercer of the shadow’), 
                    described as a sorcerer or as a 
                    demon by <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/VD2T5WH4"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen"/><title level="a">Studien zum abessinischen Zauberwesen</title><title level="j">Zeitschrift für Assyriologie und verwandte Gebiete</title><author><forename>William Hoyt</forename><surname>Worrell</surname></author><date>1914_1915</date><biblScope unit="volume">29</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">85-141</biblScope><note type="url">http://menadoc.bibliothek.uni-halle.de/dmg/periodical/titleinfo/118379</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen</note><citedRange unit="page">136</citedRange></bibl> and 
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/H8WBU22B"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1972Wellcome"/><title level="a">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts of the Wellcome Institute of the History of Medicine in London</title><title level="j">Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies, University of London</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><date>1972</date><biblScope unit="volume">35</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">1</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">27-55</biblScope><note type="url">http://www.jstor.org/stable/612793</note><citedRange unit="page">52</citedRange></bibl>.</p></abstract>
